1️⃣7️⃣ Codegen vs Manual Script Writing
Codegen & Manual script
-----------------------
1. Automatically generates code  , Written by developer
2. Fast for beginners , Better for frameworks
3. Useful for locator discovery , More optimized code

1️⃣8️⃣ Real Project Usage
In real projects , Codegen is mainly used for:
    1. Finding element locators
    2. Quickly generating action steps
    3. Debugging element selection
But frameworks are usally written manually.
